snippet.title: Assassin’s Creed Valhalla: Eivor’s Fate - Character Trailer
snippet.description:
As Eivor, embark on a quest for glory, power and prosperity. Your journey will take you far from your home - and it could cost you everything.

 Assassin’s Creed Valhalla available 17th November 2020 on Xbox One, PlayStation®4 system, Epic Games, Uplay & Stadia.
 Also coming to Xbox Series X and PlayStation®5. Pre-order now at https://www.assassinscreed.com/buy

Pre-order now and get an additional mission: The Way of the Berserker

2WEI - “Rattle and Run (Valhalla Remix)” - https://smarturl.it/acv-rar
